            <div class="events-page">

                <div class="event-post">
                    <h2>Wine & Brew 2016</h2>
                    <p class="lead">November 12th</p>
                    <p class="lead">6:30PM to 10:00PM</p>
                    <p>We would like to welcome you to Wine & Brew 2016. It will be held on November 12 at the Connell Community Center. This event was started to help cottage businesses promote themselves and make contacts within the community; all while doing so in a fun social environment with good food, drink, and music. The table space is free to you. We offer an 8 foot table for you to display your business or we can split that with another business and offer you a 4 foot space. The Chamber will advertise you and the event in the graphic and around town at no cost to you.</p>
                    <a href="~/Downloads/Registration for Wine and Brew.docx" class="btn btn-primary">Register For This Event</a>
                </div><hr />

